---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="My first post | Julio Cesar">
  <main>
    <a href="/personal_blog/blog" class="back">← Back to blog</a>
    <article>
      <span class="date">2025-11-15</span>
      <h1>My first post</h1>
      <div class="tags">
        <span>#Data Engineering</span>
        <span>#Personal</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>
          Welcome to my blog! Here I'll share my experiences as a Data Engineer,
          tutorials about PySpark, dbt, and everything related to the data world.
        </p>
        <h2>What will you find here?</h2>
        <p>
          I'll write about pipeline optimization, best practices in Databricks,
          and solutions to common problems I encounter in my day-to-day work.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'll also explore topics at the intersection of my physics background
          and data — including quantum computing and its potential applications
          in machine learning and optimization.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
<style>
  main {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .back {
    color: #bc52ee;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .back:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  article {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .date {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #111827;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }
  .tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .tags span {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #bc52ee;
  }
  .content p {
    color: #4b5563;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .content h2 {
    color: #111827;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>